

# VERBOSITY
/run/verbose 1
/event/verbose 1
/tracking/verbose 1
/process/em/verbose 1
## Making sure electroluminescence is turned on


# GENERATION
/Generator/IonGenerator/region  FIELDCAGE
/Generator/IonGenerator/atomic_number 82
/Generator/IonGenerator/mass_number 210



## Nexus Physics List
/PhysicsList/Nexus/clustering           true
/PhysicsList/Nexus/drift                true
/PhysicsList/Nexus/electroluminescence  true

