#Active
/Geometry/CRAB/Active_diam 8.5 cm
/Geometry/CRAB/Active_length 42 cm

#SourceEncloser
/Geometry/CRAB/SourceEn_diam 10 mm
/Geometry/CRAB/SourceEn_holedi 5 mm
/Geometry/CRAB/SourceEn_offset 5.7 cm



